\left(\begin{matrix}         1 & 1 & ... & 1\\         1 & 2 & ... & n \\         \end{matrix}\right) \left(\begin{matrix}         x_1 \\         \vdots \\         x_n         \end{matrix}\right) =\left(\begin{matrix}         M-r\\         M         \end{matrix}\right) 
\left(\frac{M(n-1)}{n}\right)
M
